{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/InfinitySweeper.png?t=1737307482\" /><strong>Minesweeper gone rogue!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Infinity Sweeper</strong> is a fresh and exciting twist on the classic Minesweeper concept, blending strategy, rogue-lite mechanics, and endless challenges into one thrilling experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fans of Minesweeper will instantly recognize the grid-based gameplay but will quickly discover a whole new world of danger, rewards, and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/Sequence_01_3.gif?t=1737307482\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">While uncapping tiles and avoiding sudden hazards just trying to stay alive, it\u2019s a smartness, quickness test!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/featuers.png?t=1737307482\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A Modern Twist on Minesweeper</strong>: Classic mechanics reimagined with rogue-lite elements and fresh challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Endless Replayability</strong>: Procedurally generated levels ensure every run is unique.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Grid-Based Gameplay</strong>: Outsmart traps, defeat enemies, and collect rewards to power up for future runs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rogue-lite Progression</strong>: Build your arsenal and skills to delve deeper into the infinite void.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenging Yet Rewarding</strong>: Perfect for fans of puzzle games, strategy games, and rogue-lite enthusiasts alike. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/Sequence_01_4.gif?t=1737307482\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make use of the in-depth stats screen to view your weak points and <i><strong>win a higher score each time!</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/gameplay.png?t=1737307482\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whether you're a nostalgic fan of Minesweeper or a lover of modern indie rogue-lites, <strong>Infinity Sweeper</strong> delivers a unique and addictive experience that will keep you coming back for more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/Sequence_01_5.gif?t=1737307482\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Stay alive, uncover tiles, and mark hazards in this game. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/extras/Sequence_01_6.gif?t=1737307482\" /></h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737307482","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/page.bg.jpg?t=1737307482","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/a19346860e2dcfb7f83626dfa5d2918eef0303f3/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737307482","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161400/a19346860e2dcfb7f83626dfa5d2918eef0303f3/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737307482","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Steam Leader